{"tid":341542,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"自從有左淘寶之後，出街覺得所有野都係淘寶貨","createTime":"2017-07-31T00:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T13:21:22.000Z","uid":126689,"like":384,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a074853d8096a3861b74ae7da929900b38471d01","tid":341542,"uid":126689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T00:46:27.000Z","msg":"有無人平時淘開寶既，一出街連野都唔想買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且會對出面賣既價錢好敏感<br />\n<br />\n硬係成日覺得出面買野有一大部分既錢比左業主，覺得自己會買貴<br />\n無論係衫褲、袋、飾物、手機用品、日用品、家具都會淨係想淘<br />\n得返野食、電腦、化妝品唔係淘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無淘癮深既朋友一齊傾計？<br />\n開左個淘寶telegram group 有三百幾人，一齊互相淘毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/DJckM0GdLANQhSX_K8-kEQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FDJckM0GdLANQhSX_K8-kEQ&d=dGuZikqhVjJsCjegsLqG349%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=97c54fdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/DJckM0GdLANQhSX_K8-kEQ</a>"},{"pid":"b81712121673124ab381265cf86314e46e9d3673","tid":341542,"uid":93202,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T01:35:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全覺<br />\n但深水埗偶爾會搵到比淘寶賣平少少嘅價錢"},{"pid":"ffc76f79932bff4e11e40d4ae7a95f90c059afbd","tid":341542,"uid":53223,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T01:39:19.000Z","msg":"所以已經好耐冇係街消費"},{"pid":"0f2072a3e5604bc9e954f58e4ae86f9a9056e285","tid":341542,"uid":1085,"like":9,"dislike":6,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T01:41:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7802acc258cb1b53735c2d17dba0abad21a6490b","tid":341542,"uid":126689,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T01:44:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全覺<br />\n但深水埗偶爾會搵到比淘寶賣平少少嘅價錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSSP 福仁真係平過淘寶，不過唔係全部貨<br />\n<br />\n我預期可能一段時間後，倚賴淘寶既程度高左，d野就唔會再咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過都仲係平過本地零零售<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9236d39885b400d5e68dd303a9d7e4904cbc7d","tid":341542,"uid":126689,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T01:45:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男裝衫有d偏向大陸style，著過成個大陸仔咁。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我女裝反而大部份葵廣藍田見到既都係淘寶見到<br />\n因為佢地入既本身已經係大陸貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94862bd53f675380cfb566a6d335372a04acd9c7","tid":341542,"uid":109650,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T01:46:35.000Z","msg":"成日覺得淘電子野會爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e6ad2d05341783cb730f893e57bc527d9f0486","tid":341542,"uid":62384,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T01:47:15.000Z","msg":"電話套電話殼全部都係"},{"pid":"29a25b982daef7c592a372c50a6ca77a26fc1bcc","tid":341542,"uid":281,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T01:48:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77d5aade1ed758b8ebd036b853e3de1814cc17d5","tid":341542,"uid":126689,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T01:51:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寵物店先誇，貓砂盆淘記$68賣$198<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能寵物店都比批發食左一層水呢"},{"pid":"e5e5c4bf99cfbf3bfd88a6e393016f4c82a93636","tid":341542,"uid":93202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T01:54:57.000Z","m