/blockquote><br />\n<br />\n例如？</blockquote><br />\n冇乜例如，我買外國品牌多，淘寶外國野多數貴過香港"},{"pid":"98a67baca0f7e32541edde3f723c448dbe97c05c","tid":341542,"uid":126689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:47:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔覺，平時買開啲野，淘寶冇，就算有質素都差好遠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n例如？</blockquote><br />\n冇乜例如，我買外國品牌多，淘寶外國野多數貴過香港</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n介紹下有咩正野買啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男仔背囊？"},{"pid":"31dad61f7854e475e65cef620ba75b6aa384de5f","tid":341542,"uid":35429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T02:59:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男裝衫有d偏向大陸style，著過成個大陸仔咁。</blockquote><br />\n但其實cheap之堡啲衫好多一睇就知係淘寶啲大陸style嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff2e0f21538bfb94361d4806d438bbad4e0d17d6","tid":341542,"uid":87988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T03:21:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>男裝衫有d偏向大陸style，著過成個大陸仔咁。</blockquote><br />\n但其實cheap之堡啲衫好多一睇就知係淘寶啲大陸style嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多類似既街鋪小店都係同一個貨源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55418b12de97e6d5b9ef951318c7b689480fea3","tid":341542,"uid":26110,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T03:24:32.000Z","msg":"我上淘寶睇d lego<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正版價錢差唔多<br />\n老番 就勁平，睇d 人評價既圖片，同正版差唔多<br />\n我依家買左盒黎試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96109dfb59df112d2d5f5a487e405307fa25fcde","tid":341542,"uid":59929,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T03:26:36.000Z","msg":"衫著開外國牌子<br />\n用品用開日本牌子<br />\n極少野需要淘寶上買<br />\n除左電話配件"},{"pid":"92ad3a9de68e33b1c2