27f8","tid":341542,"uid":60376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:20:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似聽人講過<br />\n<br />\n同一樣質素既野，你係淘寶可以用50%既價錢買到<br />\n<br />\n你用係街買既同一個價錢，係淘寶就可以買到更高質素既野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ncheap野細件大量生產果d就係，唔駛好高價錢，過3舊水既產品quality已經拍唔住日製台製美製<br />\n<br />\n普通生活用品就會淘 ，衫褲呢d野一舊水大把選擇啦，唔好話電子野"},{"pid":"8e8a68ba238469392e303c9a28378a56d5484ccb","tid":341542,"uid":101961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c0364f24b7fd90f6488c5e55db061062249cc32","tid":341542,"uid":59580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:23:40.000Z","msg":"入唔到個 tg"},{"pid":"60de62c88a27fc87e83ad53916cb8e2a8916c0b9","tid":341542,"uid":29514,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:24:34.000Z","msg":"上amazon買又平又高質,支那人先上淘寶"},{"pid":"1b05386b660bffe2cc82371bb240d95d648c8943","tid":341542,"uid":117458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:28:42.000Z","msg":"其實去舖頭買衫係貪佢有得試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374550664f3fe6bcb82dd2ba5f54d65d915e37f0","tid":341542,"uid":8157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:33:55.000Z","msg":"買d立雜野，配件個d一係ssp一係淘寶架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8dba3be1e1456df7ecbb4a3bb3651c92d3c0802","tid":341542,"uid":14442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:38:42.000Z","msg":"條link入唔到嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba040cafd3cd138583b7d62cd59cb35dc02ce08c","tid":341542,"uid":37723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:41:28.000Z","msg":"淘寶做起左客源既會越來越貴<br />\n新加入既就平價搶生意 <br />\n亦有D一直打平民價貨品 (始終大陸窮人多) <br />\n<br />\n所以根本香港鋪頭點打都輸"},{"pid":"f5434c975be4ab1fb26c7f2084879ad48f612afb","tid":341542,"uid":41944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:55:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人平時淘開寶既，一出街連野都唔想買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且會對出面賣既價錢好敏感<br />\n<br />\n硬係成日覺得出面買野有一大部分既錢比左業主，覺得自己會買貴<br />\n無論係衫褲、袋、飾物、手機用品、日用品、家具都會淨係想淘<br />\n得返野食、電腦、化妝品唔係淘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無淘癮深既朋友一齊傾計？<br />\n開左個淘寶telegram group 有三百幾人，一齊互相淘毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/DJckM0GdLANQhSX_K8-kEQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FDJckM0GdLANQhSX_K8-kEQ&d=dGuZikqhVjJsCjegsLqG349%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=97c54fdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/DJckM0GdLANQhSX_K8-kEQ</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsame!!!<br />\n唔想俾錢地產霸權賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07426f9a46e23a7b881078a5754d706666b4cbe3","tid":341542,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:56:45.000Z","msg":"最近買左啲衫 都係越南做"},{"pid":"15c520df21b5833022e7e5b2cb54715b1fd7f614","tid":341542,"uid":93202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:57:56.000Z","msg":"香港價錢貴又貴啲<br />\n態度又閪啲<br />\n真係諗唔到原因要幫襯, 除非件野好趕用, 否則都唔會用<br />\n之前買野趕3日後用, 計埋集運落到黎岩岩好第3日, 慳左70%錢, 快靚正"},{"pid":"e3b0b8699ad99f2b29a0c762c27296c9ef09bb9b","tid":341542,"uid":93202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T11:58:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港價錢貴又貴啲<br />\n態度又閪啲<br />\n真係諗唔到原因要幫襯, 除非件野好趕用, 否則都唔會<span style=\"color: red;\">係香港買</span><br />\n之前買野趕3日後用, 計埋集運落到黎岩岩好第3日, 慳左70%錢, 快靚正</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5b8f42f39448d100f39cc0cf97efd37297dadadd","tid":341542,"uid":35323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T12:01: