e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:27:43.000Z","msg":"電腦用品係淘寶買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以問下賣家問題 <br />\n如果去黃金買條USB線 問多兩句 隨時黑面"},{"pid":"f470dd0b02885b289faf29fc74386407c7575809","tid":341542,"uid":12265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T13:30:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寵物店先誇，貓砂盆淘記$68賣$198<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鋪租貴麻，所以好多時唔好用網店同實體鋪比，唔岩價返屋企慢慢上網搵好野算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c314b787d88ec6ddfa4679edb736c828e7e453a7","tid":341542,"uid":38472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"舖頭賣咁貴，係要承受鋪租，人工，同件貨品質嘅風險，所以都好正常。<br />\n<br />\n不過班大商家又係奶共，啲錢都係比支共，所以同款係淘寶買唔會比支共食多啲錢。"},{"pid":"ba12b3d0439f4e97f3748a5b4ffa5c11d87b234d","tid":341542,"uid":24335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T14:05:09.000Z","msg":"真係, 有時明知唔幫襯返香港鋪頭會造成惡性循環(細鋪因為租貴同冇生意不停執, 最後剩低大集團連鎖店), 但係一望個價錢真係買唔落手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c0d44d79a50edd200d6e1bbb9b26aa42aa0794f","tid":341542,"uid":62734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:33:29.000Z","msg":"認真一問<br />\n依家重入唔入得 gp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想睇吓有冇咩岩淘既屎"},{"pid":"356ba2d81c3f52bc4936007e478e078b902f9ad8","tid":341542,"uid":112969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:36:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買啲廢野家品野垃雜野貪玩野，就一定淘寶<br />\n另外有野想訂造都會淘寶<br />\n售前服務好，有心機有禮貌<br />\n售後就改不了支那種，閪閪地，不過都好過香港<br />\n<br />\n想買有牌子既，例如電子產品，電子周邊，衫褲鞋襪，電器<br />\n大可以上樂天，amazon，其他英國美國網<br />\n大部分平過香港<br />\n佢地啲售後仲要癲既，好似倒米咁<br />\n啱啱買左條短褲，速遞紀錄有問題<br />\n我只係問左一句，佢即刻寄多條比我，雖然只係百幾蚊<br />\n比著香港，十蚊貨仔都會留難你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺ssp，旺角，油麻地呢啲地方會搵到平過網購既，自己去開熟路知價，就會喺呢啲鋪頭買<br />\n不過數埋都唔夠十間，其餘一律上網禁<br />\n基本上杯葛左香港零售架喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n美國 英國網有咩介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d7eeb73ee8e682b7003a07cadddca76e91d7f7","tid":341542,"uid":97330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:38:04.000Z","msg":"依家唔入得group啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"0179b6b04f1494ca2f9fe11fbab06a8ededea25b","tid":341542,"uid":70293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:47:59.000Z","msg":"wa diu"},{"pid":"bf5107b40472ab48db7ff25464bc5bf32d1bc787","tid":341542,"uid":2059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T16:00:56.000Z","msg":"原來係佣金狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"827026cd273b1831cb1903c13879b539f7480fa3","tid":341542,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T16:12:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主咁熱心 因為佢每一單都有回佣架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pe5gq41m\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpe5gq41m&h=037b93c2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母 佣金狗生性病死全家</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5e5175a6623f3e37174a6a00bf11476b1b961fd4","tid":341542,"uid":48834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T16:49:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>買啲廢野家品野垃雜野貪玩野，就一定淘寶<br />\n另外有野想訂造都會淘寶<br />\n售前服務好，有心機有禮貌<br />\n售後就改不了支那種，閪閪地，不過都好過香港<br />\n<br />\n想買有牌子既，例如電子產品，電子周邊，衫褲鞋襪，電器<br />\n大可以上樂天，amazon，其他英國美國網<br />\n大部分平過香港<br />\n佢地啲售後仲要癲既，好似倒米咁<br />\n啱啱買左條短褲，速遞紀錄有問題<br />\n我只係問左一句，佢即刻寄多條比我，雖然只係百幾蚊<br />\n比著香港，十蚊貨仔都會留難你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺ss